89, 155.402, 156.6287, 155.6052, 157.4852, 156.7053, 156.8537, 157.0811, 156.8623, 157.3059, 157.7854, 158.0234, 157.4527, 160.2363, 158.9095, 159.3766, 161.4193, 161.9848, 160.6211, 161.425, 157.4528, 158.0201, 158.0497, 158.0227, 157.8099, 157.9416, 156.5075, 156.5379, 155.769, 156.4003, 156.3922, 156.9659, 157.2224, 156.4958, 156.6171, 156.0215, 154.761, 154.2365, 153.673, 156.7335, 159.2267, 158.5045, 160.5014, 160.1984, 157.9781, 159.752, 158.3699, 157.0023, 156.0897, 155.2369, 154.3699, 155.1948, 154.9851, 155.0721, 155.617, 154.0469, 153.0375, 154.8698, 154.1047, 152.8903, 152.0167, 152.1499, 151.807, 151.8854, 151.2403, 150.5669, 149.5585, 149.1431, 148.8291, 149.3683, 149.3643, 149.4748, 149.6269, 149.2552, 148.0213, 147.7733, 147.7631, 147.5202, 147.3775, 147.3796, 146.7383, 146.352, 147.4231, 148.871, 149.0355, 150.4666, 150.2317, 150.5044, 151.5485, 151.2298, 151.0917, 150.2692, 149.788, 150.7968, 151.8781, 153.1538, 152.4407, 152.2181, 152.724, 152.0643, 150.4759, 151.3816, 151.179, 149.5425, 147.8993, 148.9209, 147.7671, 148.3367, 147.902, 146.3802, 146.1565, 145.4714, 145.4529, 145.4174, 145.7129, 146.109, 146.8687, 146.853, 146.1055, 145.39, 145.9689, 146.2581, 145.7136, 145.4526, 146.6458, 146.1372, 146.4174, 147.1473, 146.8622, 146.3922, 146.6951, 146.5009, 147.6567, 146.8457, 146.5236, 148.8665, 149.6369, 150.3633, 150.0428, 149.9068, 149.2965, 149.1852, 147.487, 145.9873, 146.9594, 148.0023, 147.8113, 147.9205, 146.2766, 146.956, 147.9658, 149.7773, 152.9982, 153.5522, 152.0163, 152.6734, 154.8335, 155.6676, 157.2791, 157.0579, 154.766, 155.2756, 156.273, 157.1542, 156.3247, 160.2027, 160.9065, 161.3721, 162.8103, 163.9363, 161.3007, 156.6966, 157.5762, 158.1782, 156.8406, 157.8863, 159.099, 159.8679, 161.0872, 159.6392, 160.5791, 162.9513, 162.9176, 161.9272, 162.6318, 167.8595, 168.6958, 168.7193, 170.4088, 172.8159, 178.1957, 171.9784, 174.6841, 175.8231, 175.741, 178.3105, 178.5166, 183.339, 183.7088, 180.6784, 178.397, 179.3698, 177.0292, 179.5557, 181.5651, 180.1535, 180.5948, 179.2795], "summary_html": "<h1>Vol Surprise Factor -- Sharpe 1.36 (通过)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本论文研究了 COVID-19 大流行对全球股票市场的分形传染效应，发现波动率在危机期间呈现显著的跨市场联动，但这种传染效应会随时间\"逐渐消退\"(fizzle out)。论文使用 DMCA/DCCA 去趋势交叉相关分析方法，比较了\"平静期\"和\"疫情期\"的波动率跨相关结构变化。</p>\n<p>基于论文中\"条件波动率 vs 无条件波动率\"的核心对比思路，我们构建了 <strong>Vol Surprise 因子</strong>：用较长窗口的已实现波动率(realized vol)除以 GARCH(1,1) 条件波动率，衡量波动率的\"意外程度\"。当已实现波动率相对于 GARCH 预测偏低时（低 surprise），说明市场处于可预测的趋势状态，因子做多；反之当已实现波动率远超 GARCH 预测时（高 surprise），说明市场处于传染/混乱状态，因子做空。该因子本质上是一个波动率 regime 指标，捕捉了论文所揭示的\"传染效应随时间消退\"现象——在条件波动率能够良好预测的市场环境中获利。</p>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>核心信号定义：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{vol\\_surprise}_t = \\frac{\\sigma^{RV}_{t,W}}{\\sigma^{GARCH}_{t}}</div>\n<p>其中：</p>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma^{RV}_{t,W}</span> 为窗口 <span class=\"math-tex\">W</span> 天的已实现波动率（对数收益率的 rolling std）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma^{GARCH}_{t}</span> 为 GARCH(1,1) 模型的条件波动率（rolling window=252, refit_every=20）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>仓位构建：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_t = \\text{CrossSectionalRank}(-\\text{vol\\_surprise}_t)</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_t = (\\text{rank}_t - 0.5) \\times 2.0</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_t = \\text{signal}_t \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{target}}{\\sigma^{RV}_{t,60} \\times \\sqrt{252}}</div>\n<h2>参数列表</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>默认值</th><th>范围</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td>rvol_window</td><td>180</td><td>[60, 504]</td><td>已实现波动率计算窗口（最优=180）</td></tr><tr><td>garch_window</td><td>252</td><td>[252, 504]</td><td>GARCH 拟合窗口</td></tr><tr><td>garch_refit</td><td>20</td><td>[10, 40]</td><td>GARCH 重拟合间隔</td></tr><tr><td>hold_days</td><td>5</td><td>[3, 20]</td><td>再平衡周期</td></tr><tr><td>vol_target</td><td>0.15</td><td>[0.05, 0.30]</td><td>年化波动率目标</td></tr><tr><td>max_leverage</td><td>2.0</td><td>[1.0, 5.0]</td><td>最大杠杆</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (扣费后)</td><td><strong>1.364</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益率</td><td>114.8%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动率</td><td>84.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-33.4%</td></tr><tr><td>NAV终值</td><td>10.85</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手率</td><td>1.69</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>前 5 变体对比</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>变体</th><th>Sharpe</th><th>年化收益</th><th>最大回撤</th></tr><tr><td>vs180_h5_raw</td><td>1.364</td><td>114.8%</td><td>-33.4%</td></tr><tr><td>vs252_h7_raw</td><td>1.194</td><td>99.9%</td><td>-48.0%</td></tr><tr><td>vs180_h5_cs</td><td>1.126</td><td>229.7%</td><td>-41.0%</td></tr><tr><td>vs252_h7_cs</td><td>1.103</td><td>230.5%</td><td>-42.6%</td></tr><tr><td>vs200_h5_cs</td><td>1.073</td><td>221.1%</td><td>-44.5%</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe 分解</strong> (最优变体):</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.03</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.01</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.03</span></td><td>0.59</td><td>0.37</td><td>0.59</td><td>0.14</td><td>0.31</td><td>0.28</td><td>0.25</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>IC 统计</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li>截面 IC = 0.0178, ICIR = 0.085</li>\n<li>时序 IC = 0.0163, ICIR = 0.437, IC&gt;0 品种占 75.4%</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<h3>R1: 初始实现（Sharpe 1.333）</h3>\n<p>构建三类因子：vol_surprise（rvol/GARCH）、garch_regime（EWMA/rvol）、kalman_beta_mom（Kalman速度 * 动量）。共 10 个变体。结果显示 vol_surprise 系列表现优异（w252=1.33, w120=1.16, w60=0.90），而 garch_regime（-0.14~0.30）和 kalman_mom（-0.29~0.05）表现不佳。核心发现：rvol/GARCH 比值作为截面因子有效，窗口越长表现越好。</p>\n<h3>R2: 聚焦 vol_surprise + hold/IC 优化（Sharpe 1.307）</h3>\n<p>去掉无效的 kalman_mom 和 garch_regime，专注 vol_surprise。测试 hold=10/20 降换手、IC gate 过滤弱品种、GJR-GARCH 非对称波动率。结果：hold=20 降低了换手率（1.64-&gt;0.82）但增大回撤（-35%-&gt;-60%），Sharpe 略降。_cs 归一化表现不错（~1.09），IC gate 和 GJR 无显著改善。</p>\n<h3>R3: 参数 grid 搜索（Sharpe 1.364, 新高）</h3>\n<p>对 rvol 窗口（180/200/252/300/504）和 hold（3/5/7）做 grid 搜索。关键发现：rvol=180 比 rvol=252 更优（1.36 vs 1.33），较短的 rvol 窗口对波动率 regime 变化更敏感，hold=5 维持最优。最终选择 vs180_h5_raw 作为最优配置。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全部商品期货（57个活跃品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 5天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>核心依赖</strong>: <code>arch</code> 库（GARCH 拟合）</li>\n<li><strong>计算量</strong>: GARCH per-symbol 拟合较慢（约 20-30 秒/轮）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 2017-2018 年 Sharpe 接近零，因子在低波动环境效果有限\n<p>- 换手率 1.69 偏高，实盘需考虑滑点 - 因子对 rvol 窗口参数敏感（180 vs 252 差异明显），可能存在过拟合风险 - 冗余检查 max_corr=0.43（与 inv120 因子），verdict=marginal</p>"}